    "description": "该模板是GameCreator官方出品的游戏模板-《梦之剑》。可用于可视化制作回合制战斗的游戏。<br>该模板包含了GameCreator引擎的功能以及模板独有的核心系统以及编辑器。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/28722f816b58c7520d98bb32f5ba396b.avif?t=1750162809\" width=620 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏手柄和SteamDeck支持</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/20ea350dd850b3d87d03523667d6a290.avif?t=1750162809\" width=620 height=272 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗演示</h2>以下为部分的战斗演示效果<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/35bdfb8b9ee58217936a8a43bf6867b7.poster.avif?t=1750162809\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/35bdfb8b9ee58217936a8a43bf6867b7.webm?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/35bdfb8b9ee58217936a8a43bf6867b7.mp4?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/b48b20866a24eeeff4eb2ee2fb7cec84.poster.avif?t=1750162809\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/b48b20866a24eeeff4eb2ee2fb7cec84.webm?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/b48b20866a24eeeff4eb2ee2fb7cec84.mp4?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/89e2913b5d7a3f97a2b4f54858436c59.poster.avif?t=1750162809\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/89e2913b5d7a3f97a2b4f54858436c59.webm?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/89e2913b5d7a3f97a2b4f54858436c59.mp4?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/50a68b42170e2bc6b77191efc720ead0.poster.avif?t=1750162809\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/50a68b42170e2bc6b77191efc720ead0.webm?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/50a68b42170e2bc6b77191efc720ead0.mp4?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/cb789fe596b78778798f12dde8a2015a.poster.avif?t=1750162809\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/cb789fe596b78778798f12dde8a2015a.webm?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187430/extras/cb789fe596b78778798f12dde8a2015a.mp4?t=1750162809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色与职业</h2>多角色养成与自由设置职业，允许设置可自由解散的队员，允许将角色设置成电脑操控。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备系统</h2>携带后可附加自动状态、免疫状态等的特殊设置，也可设置随机浮动属性。<br>可以设置装备的佩戴和卸下时的事件，方便制作一些特殊效果。<br>自由设置部位（如头部、身体、武器）以及装备的类别（如剑、锤、法杖等）<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能系统</h2>技能提供了非常多的参数可供设置，比如：<br>发射弹幕、冷却时间、连击、多目标攻击、被动技能等等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >状态系统</h2>可拥有控制类的状态、叠加层数、DOT/HOT、属性加成等等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗系统</h2>· 自由控制战斗的发生或中断。<br>· 支持纯自动战斗<br>· 允许战败后触发剧情<br>· 允许设置攻击友军<br>· 允许设置在不满足条件时仍然派发指令，当实际行动时若满足条件了则允许行动。<br>· 允许使用道具来释放一次性的技能<br>· 允许可视化设置我方与敌方的人数与站位等等<br>· 允许可视化设置动态战斗背景<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内置素材</h2>包含所有苍之羽的素材以及该模板独有的素材，如多种立绘、数十个战斗角色和动画等等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高级扩展</h2>由于引擎支持插件与脚本，可以在模板基础上任意扩展。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用该模板制作的部分游戏</h2>《异常情绪回收组》：<br>《浮世万千三天地情殇》：<br><br>更多特性，待您体验！",
